Merge pull request #28 from ritstudentgovernment/add-missing-courses

Add online courses; landing page ui changes

alternate landing page media icon layout

Creates more visual balance on landing page.

improved section matching algorithm

When associating students with their enrolled sections, first attempt
to make an exact match; if one cannot be found, fall back on a more
loosely defined regex match.

pull online sections in data feed

Supply some additional options into the data feed API to make sure all
sections for a term are loaded.

Merge pull request #27 from ritstudentgovernment/course-integration-fixes

Course integration fixes

Add missing sections to user - fixes #23

Use a regular expression to more loosely match the appropriate section
a student is enrolled in, due to data format integration issues between
the `ELASTICSEARCH_ENDPOINT` and `COURSEDATA_ENDPOINT`.

Non-blocking publications; restrict jobs API access

It appears the `meteor-job-collection` security policies aren’t
functioning correctly, so check the user’s role type in job api calls.

better section type identification

Prefer a regex match over substring match; show section type on
evaluations (‘write a review’) page
